   <text>
      <front>
         <div type="tipografia" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
            <p rend="writing-mode(horizontal-lr) text-orientation(sideways)" part="N">
               <s> Proprietà artistica riservata </s>
            </p>
         </div>
      </front>
      <body>
         <div type="fronte" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
            <figure>
               <head>Preghiera per l'assente</head>
               <figDesc> Donna con mani giunte in preghiera
               </figDesc>
            </figure>
         </div>
         <div type="retro">
            <div type="message">
               <opener>
                  <dateline>
                     <lb/>
                     <s>            Formigine lì 1/3 - 1918</s>
                  </dateline>
               </opener>
               <div type="postcard-body">
                  <p type="retro">
                     <lb/>            Oliva mia, quando mi coglie tristezza tetra <lb/>            come altra notte, sento acutissimo<lb/>            tutto il dolore d'un amore soffer - <lb/>            to nel cuore e nell'anima che non <lb/>            può sbocciare al sole nascente, non <lb/>            scaldarsi alla fiamma dolcezza del <lb/>            tramonto, non espandersi non <lb/>            obligarti all'affetto, ai tuoi <gap reason="illegible"/>
                     <lb/>            alle più piccole, pallide e rosee, ardenti <lb/>            e luminose sfumature del sentimento. <lb/>            Tu mi manchi affannatamente, tu <lb/>            sei lontana, lontana, che fai? Che <lb/>            pensi? Non senti un grido d'amo - <lb/>            re che rompe dal petto mio e <lb/>            ti invoca in un anelito posfente  <lb/>            di vita, di bene, di felicità, di bontà ?<lb/>            Che fai tu ora? Dove sei? Perchè <lb/>            non mi è data la suprema gioia <lb/>            della vita degli occhi tuoi, del fremito <lb/>            delle tue carezze? T'amo? Amami!!...</p>
                  <p type="fronte"/>
               </div>
               <closer>
                  <lb/>
                  <signed>
                     <persName>
                        <forename ref="Giovannino">Giovannino</forename>
                     </persName>
                  </signed>
               </closer>
            </div>
            <div type="postmark-postage">
               <ab/>
            </div>
            <div type="secondamano">
               <ab type="paratext" part="N">
                  <add>
                     <num type="cardinal"> 201 </num>
                  </add>
               </ab>
            </div>
         </div>
      </body>
